          <mxGeometry x="54" y="410" width="160" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="3azDmyGYVqigEuWXIeZL-25" value="&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;请描述如下信息：&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; （1）、数据源类型：例如数据库（MySQL、ClickHouse）、文件、SQLElasticsearch、Kafka等。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; （2）、数据源连接信息：指出数据源的具体连接信息，如数据库服务器地址/端口、API端点等。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; （3）、数据信息：读取的数据库表、SQL语句、ES索引等&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; （4）、认证信息：说明访问数据源所需的权限和认证机制，如用户名/密码等。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; （5）、数据格式和结构：描述数据源中数据的格式和结构，包括字段名称、数据类型、关系模型等。&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="220" y="220" width="570" height="110" as="geometry" />
